<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٧٨ - ٤٧٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1262">حَامِدُ بْنُ عُمَرَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/943">بِشْرٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3055">عَاصِمٌ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6775">وَاقِدٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5618">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ، </a>أَوِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3823">ابْنِ عَمْرٍو </a>: <span class="c2">«شَبَّكَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> أَصَابِعَهُ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>